·         to make predictions about your characteristics, interests or preferences and to display targeted advertisements, deals and offers that we believe will be of interest to you;
·         to request feedback and to otherwise contact you about your use of our Sites;
·         to respond to your emails, submissions, questions, comments, requests and complaints and provide customer service;
·         to monitor and analyze usage and trends, determine the effectiveness of our advertisements and personalize and improve the Sites, such as providing ads, content or features that match users' profiles or interests and increasing the functionality and user friendliness of the Sites;
·         to send you surveys, updates, security alerts and support and administrative messages and otherwise facilitate your use of, and our administration and operation of, the Sites;
